<subSubSection pageId="193" pageNumber="796" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="193.[778,1370,2112,2534]" pageId="193" pageNumber="796">Placed in subgenus Pyromys by J. T. Mar- shall in 1977. There are no genetic data currently available to clarify its relation- ships. Monotypic.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
